title: Message from the LPC Chair – Ted Brown (Libertarian Party of California)
text: ( Source : Libertarian Party of California ) Dear California LP Members, I want to keep you updated about what's going on in the Libertarian Party of California. The 2016 state convention will be held on April 1, 2 , & 3 at the LAX Hilton
